      "id": "PopularPost165128",
      "post_content": "Why debate which is better between two solid cards?  \nBoth are certainly better than [Rod of Ruin](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Rod of Ruin), nuff said.  \nPlay both, and for a total of 12 mana spent, you get 26 damage to whatever roaming around in you deck.  \nFits nicely in just about any burn style I can think of.",
