      "id": "PopularPost160504",
      "post_content": "Context is everything. Remember that Tempest saw the introduction of [Shock](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Shock) as a 'fair' [Lightning Bolt](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Lightning Bolt). This was also the era of [Incinerate](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Incinerate) as the 3 damage spell of choice.",
      "posted_by": "Equinox523",
